title: Cilent Doesnt Launch
body: when league of legends is opened.. i click launch... nothing happens... i havent played league for more then a month or two due to problems arising after every update.

replies.body: Most of the time this happens because your OS blocks the program from opening. Without the right permissions, your OS might not recognize the program that's trying to open and then your OS thinks it might be dangerous. Hit up our [**permission guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) to make sure you can open League without it being stopped.
